# otjni

Demo code to show the connection from Clojure to OT

## Usage

lein run script.run

## Installation on Linux

Fix Makefile.API (line 269):
JAVA_INCLUDEDIRS = -I/usr/$(LINUX_LIBDIR)/jvm/java-6-sun/include -I/usr/$(LINUX_LIBDIR)/jvm/java-6-sun/include/linux

Build Open Transactions:

make clean
make java

Copy libotapi.so to the jni folder of otjni.

